The Federal Reserve is the bank of the State.
The SMR is the bank of the Earth.
PART III: THE UNIT (GFR)
The SMR is the mountain. But you cannot carry a mountain in your pocket.
To make this wealth usable for humanity, the SMR issues a Geo-Fiduciary Receipt.
This receipt is called GFR.
GFR is The People’s Gram.
One gram of SMR inventory is the atomic constant. It represents 1 gram of audited, in-situ mineral wealth (Gold, Platinum, Lithium, Nickel).
However, a single gram is too heavy for daily trade. If we traded in full grams, the poor would be excluded, left holding dust.
To ensure velocity and utility for every human on Earth, the SMR executes a Permanent Split at issuance.
The Eternal Ratio
1 Earth Gram (SMR) = 100,000 GFR.
This ratio is fixed. It is eternal.
There are no decimals. There is no "dust."
There is only GFR.
When GFR moves, it carries Sovereign Value (SV).
"Sovereign Value" is the natural language of the protocol. It is the quality of the money you hold. When you hold GFR, you hold receipts of Sovereign Value.
You spend whole numbers. You save whole numbers.
Children do not count decimals. Elders do not calculate fractions.
People trade whole values like breath.
The split happened once. It never happens again. The gram lives eternally.
