If a corrupt official or a foreign syndicate tries to seize that land, they are attacking the assets of the entire Gold Air network.
An eviction in Binga becomes a direct assault on the net worth of an investor in London. The world’s phones light up. The world’s lawyers—paid in GFR—descend on the aggressor.
